      "description": "Looking for your next rewarding project? This vehicle is a fantastic canvas for any automotive enthusiast ready to bring a classic back to life! While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a wonderful opportunity for someone who loves to get their hands dirty and restore a car to its former glory. Whether you're looking for a dedicated restoration piece or a valuable parts donor, this car is priced to move and ready for its next adventure!",
