      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest possible standards. This unit exhibits a pristine exterior and a flawless interior, reflecting a level of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market. Mechanically sound and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it represents the definitive choice for the uncompromising enthusiast.",
